<li>Add sanity to the <a href="https://man.openbsd.org/?query=apmd&amp;sektion=8">apmd(8)</a> battery alert when the battery is charging.
<li>Let <a href="https://man.openbsd.org/?query=chdir&amp;sektion=2">chdir(2)</a> errors in <a href="https://man.openbsd.org/?query=rwhod&amp;sektion=8">rwhod(8)</a> be seen.
